{"tid":137041,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同朋友放學遇到變態佬","createTime":"2017-02-27T13:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T04:25:30.000Z","uid":37989,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1108ce38a8efc5f073bb36e5ec010fedd737587c","tid":137041,"uid":37989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n我一直顧著同佢傾計冇留意到<br />\n佢要好驚咁挨埋黎我先注意到<br />\n但果陣我呆左<br />\n我未試過遇到呢啲事<br />\n我淨係好嚴肅咁問左個變態佬：你做咩事？<br />\n然後個變態佬想摸我朋友隻腳果陣我擋住同隔開左佢兩個<br />\n然後朋友就跑走左<br />\n剩番我同個變態佬兩個人企左喺度&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n事後講番 我一路同佢講自己太懦弱<br />\n佢安慰我：如果我係你女朋友 你就會更加留意四周 反應更加大會保護我 我又唔係你女朋友 好正常姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我依家個心酸溜溜的&hellip;"},{"pid":"72dad4649f0e5bed082fa60c76f2581fbd7c0871","tid":137041,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打蛇隨棍上喇"},{"pid":"f13dcb0d6694749919ff8d6822d218ef133e708d","tid":137041,"uid":37989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打蛇隨棍上喇</blockquote><br />\n即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9521562264871c21b595b8fca182866288909fff","tid":137041,"uid":340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:00:27.000Z","msg":"性暗示黎，岩聽？"},{"pid":"7be36f9cea02a2dfb3d8403f0028256526f7b9eb","tid":137041,"uid":37989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性暗示黎，岩聽？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有可能"},{"pid":"71e17d205e88b86ef5aa46c2be9e7ba49a2bed97","tid":137041,"uid":37989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T14:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"